</p>

</div>
<div id="fn" class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-02-05-02-0318-fn-0001-ptr" id="GEWN-02-05-02-0318-fn-0001">1</a>

   <p>In the original letter book GW inserted not after can and deleted little.</p>

</div>
<div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-02-05-02-0318-fn-0002-ptr" id="GEWN-02-05-02-0318-fn-0002">2</a>

   <p>See <a href="default.xqy?keys=GEWN-print-02-05-02-0311" class="document">GW to Bouquet, 13</a>, <a href="default.xqy?keys=GEWN-print-02-05-02-0320" class="document">19 August</a>.</p>

</div>
<div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-02-05-02-0318-fn-0003-ptr" id="GEWN-02-05-02-0318-fn-0003">3</a>

   <p>GW wrote is inadvertently.</p>

</div>
<div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-02-05-02-0318-fn-0004-ptr" id="GEWN-02-05-02-0318-fn-0004">4</a>

   <p>This paragraph does not appear in his letter-book copies of this letter.</p>

</div>
